{
  "chapter": 11,
  "chapter_summary": "第十一章「逃亡」。子夜，唐花带卫凤娘逃离唐家堡。唐花准备黑衣让卫凤娘换上，卫凤娘随身带剑自称学了一点剑法。两人穿过树林时遭遇两名黑衣女守卫，唐花以掌法将二人击倒。唐花假装受伤试探卫凤娘，卫凤娘真心关怀并表示愿代他承担责任。到达城门后唐花用霹雳堂炸药炸开大门，二人逃出。唐花说明下山还有最后一道关卡——唐枫、唐梅、唐桑、唐棉四位老家臣把守要道。因下雨天无法放烟花示警，二人有机会通过。途中突降大雨，二人到山神庙避雨烤火。庙中发现一堵补过的墙壁，敲开后是一条通往山外的秘道。二人通过秘道直接下山，绕过四老把守。卫凤娘暗自记住地形，想将秘道告诉赵无忌，内心感伤。二人到达小镇歇息，唐花说还需四五天才能到大风堂势力范围。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "你不是不会武功吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "以前都不会，前一阵子学了一点点剑法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "带着剑走很累赘，你..",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "没关系，这样我比较有安全感。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "待会发生什么事，你都躲在一旁，不要发出声音，知道吗？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "好，那我们走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi_yi",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣女人甲",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "什么人？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi_yi",
      "text": "是我，唐花。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi_yi",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣女人甲",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "这么晚了，你们来干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi_yi",
      "text": "这样的夜晚，谈心散步不很适宜吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "闪开！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "你受伤了吗？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "我们马上离开这里。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "你受伤了吗？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "不要紧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "血流这么多，怎么会不要紧？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "不痛，只是一点外伤而已。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "怎么办？我看先找个地方包扎一下吧。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "没关系，赶快离开这里最要紧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "你真的不要紧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "真的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "假如我伤得很重，怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "那我们就不要走，返回去等你把伤口治好了再作打算。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "万一回去被发现呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "我会把责任都推到我身上来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "唐家的人会信吗？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "别傻了，我既然决定带你走，一定会尽力把你带成功。我们还是赶快走吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "待会我要使用霹雳堂的炸药，你先躲在这儿别过来，炸完之后再冲过来，我会把门打开。记住，一切要快！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shou_wei_jia",
      "speaker_name": "守卫甲",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_shou_wei_yi",
      "text": "是我，唐花。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "又过了一关了！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "还没安全呀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "再一关就安全了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "这一关容易过吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "比以前都难。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "不要慌，也许很容易过也说不定。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "到这里为止，都是我熟悉的环境，一切好办，下一关却必须面对四个人，那四个我都熟，如果我用言语骗得过他们，也许不费吹灰之力就可以通过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "我们必须要碰到那四个人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "为什么？难道没有别的路可走吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "没有。要离开唐家堡下山，那是必经之路。除了那条路以外，就是悬崖峭壁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "别担心，今天的天气对我们有利。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "这跟天气有关？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "有。那四个人守着必经之路，不是每个人都不放行的。他们是奉命行事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "奉命？奉什么命？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "当然是奉唐家的命。唐家的规矩，只要发现有可疑的人离开，便会发放火箭烟花示警，他们看到烟花的颜色，就会把人拦截下来，或者杀了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "他们武功高强吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "很高强。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "你打得过他们吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "打不过。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "那我们干脆回去，不必冒险。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "不，要试一试运气。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "运气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "不错，今天天气很坏，不适宜放烟花，放了也不一定看得到。假如他们看不到那唐家示警烟火，我们就有机会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "真的。你看，我手掌里的是什么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "怎么啦？机会来了，你怎么反而忧愁起来呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "我在担心，我们该到哪里去躲雨。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "躲雨有什么要紧？逃出去才要紧啊！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "不，躲雨很要紧。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "为什么？淋一场雨不会生病的。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "我不是怕生病。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "那你怕什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "有人会在晚上淋着雨出城的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "当然没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "那我们怎么办？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "我们往上面走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "上面有躲雨的地方吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "应该有。假如我记得不错，上面应该有一间破落的山神庙。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "你也没来过这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "来墙边坐吧。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "这里可以靠一靠。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "怎么啦？怕雷电？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "不，我忽然想到了一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "我们应该现在离开。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "这么大的雷雨，不是逃走的最好时机吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "你怎么会这样想？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "你不是说，有四个人守在必经的路上吗？他们难道不会找地方来躲避这场雷雨？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "不会。因为他们都是尽责的人。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "尽责归尽责，总不能不躲雨吧？万一被雷打中了怎么办？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "那就只好当作是命了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "会吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "别人我不知道，这四个人一定会。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "你认为他们会站在外面任风吹雨打",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "你怎么知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "想也想得到。这样的天气，有什么人要逃离唐家堡的话，一定会加以利用，他们就一定会比平常还要加倍小心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "这是我们的家规。当然，这一代的唐家人倒不一定都遵守，但上一代的人都会彻底执行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "他们是上一代的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "不错。他们都是跟随唐傲的父亲的人，非常忠于唐家，也非常尽忠职守。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "他们是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "他们这么厉害，我们骗得了他们吗？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "很难，不过还是要试试。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "我看是没有希望了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "你怎么这样想？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "我们出城的时候，不是杀了好几个人吗？你想想看，这一定会惊动唐家堡，也一定会有人向唐枫他们示警。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "话是不错，不过，没有人知道是我们两个杀的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "这么说来，我们还有一丝希望。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "要不要去看看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "当然要。也许天无绝人之路，这是一条通往外面的暗道也说不定。",
      "tone": "期待",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "咦？不晓得这个山洞通往哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "我知道了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "你知道什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "我知道这山洞通往哪里。我小时候就曾听说过，通往唐家堡有一条秘道，后来为了安全封起来",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "为什么要封起来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "因为知道的人一多，难免会泄露出去，万一被敌人知道，岂不麻烦？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "为什么不派人看守？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "派人看守有缺点。首先你要调度人，其次，这个人的武功要高，最怕的是这个人万一被收买，那后果就不堪设想了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "那我们已经下山了？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "一点也不错。而且不必经过唐棉他们四个人的考验。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "太好了！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "下去很好走。下山以后，再走一两个时辰，就有一个小镇，我们可以在那里休息。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "去睡个觉吧，以后我们都要昼伏夜行了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "要到什么地方，我们才算安全？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "唐家堡又攻陷了三个大风堂的据点，他们的势力愈发庞大，我看，我们还要走四五天才能到达真正安全的地方。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卫凤娘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua",
      "text": "你是说大风堂的势力范围？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua",
      "speaker_name": "唐花",
      "listener": "char_wei_feng_niang",
      "text": "是的，不然，我们随时都有被捉的可能。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 11,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    }
  ],
